<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-10-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-10-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="578" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d578">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">Secretary’s Memoranda, Lot 53 D
                                444</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the <gloss type="from">Special
                                        Assistant</gloss> to the Secretary of State</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Battle</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                                </seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-10-26">October 26,
                                        1950</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p rend="flushleft">Item 6. <hi rend="italic">Israeli Loan
                                    Application</hi>
                            </p>
                            <p>The Secretary told me after his appointment with the President today,
                                that he had discussed the Israeli loan application with him, and
                                that the President had indicated he would look into the matter and
                                speak to the Secretary again. The Secretary said that meanwhile he
                                would discuss this matter with Mr. Webb.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>L[<hi rend="smallcaps">ucius</hi>] D. B[<hi rend="smallcaps">attle</hi>]</signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>